snippet.title: Shing! Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Here it is! first glimpse of Shing! gameplay. 
Action packed beat'em'up sidescroller will be available for PC [Steam], PS4, Xbox, and Nintendo Switch.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1103730/Shing/
More information on our FB: https://www.facebook.com/MassCreationGames/
http://mass-creation.com
